dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing
Class TableSelectionEvent

java.lang.Object
  dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing.WidgetSelectionEvent
      dreisoft.tresos.guidedconfig.api.gui.eventing.TableSelectionEvent

public class TableSelectionEvent
extends WidgetSelectionEvent

The event is fired as a WidgetSelectionEvent by SWTTable instances.

This event provides:

  • Row and column of the clicked cell of the last mouse click
  • Currently selected rows
